properties.Name: CustomerPartyRelationshipType
properties.Description:
The nature of the relationship between a customer and a related party.

Ex:
- Company - parent company 
- Company - subsidiary company 
- Company - company Shipping Agent
- Company - related-company
- Individual - Employer
- Individual - Family Member
- Customer Referral
- National Jurisdiction
- State Jurisdiction
- Provincial Jurisdiction
- Customer - Travel Agent
